# Dedicated CLI compile server (separate from vshaxe). Start once:
#   haxe --wait 7822
# Caches macro-expanded modules between runs (105 @:peg parsers / 22
# @:build) so only changed modules recompile. If a stale synthesized-
# type error appears, restart the server.
--connect 7822
-cp src
-cp test
-lib utest
-main RunTests
-neko bin/test.n
--cmd neko bin/test.n
